---
title: Honey-Soy Glazed Chicken Breast & Sesame Fries with Japanese-Style Pear Salad
description: This magical meal is made in a flash but tastes like hours of effort went into it. The classic combination of
honey and soy speaks for itself, while Japanese dressing on a crisp salad and sesame fries add an extra twist.
